WEBVTT

00:01.969 --> 00:08.969
We had this Ganesha Puja, and I really spoke
very nicely on equilibrium. And the rain,

01:01.370 --> 01:08.370
expressed its equilibrium, but when they were
singing, it was very quiet. And when it stopped

01:09.530 --> 01:15.720
for a short time suddenly it came with a complete
gusto and sang some songs and went away again.

01:15.720 --> 01:22.720
Just for the aarti to start with. It’s very
beautiful it was. So dramatic. Very interesting.

01:25.750 --> 01:32.750
So all preparations are done for the puja?
Maybe some people might come up from abroad,

01:41.900 --> 01:48.900
I don’t know. Maybe. Have you written to
some leaders or not, about this puja that

02:00.890 --> 02:07.890
we are going to have?
Yogi: I think yes some invitations were sent

02:08.959 --> 02:14.959
out.
Shri Mataji: Might have gone out.

02:14.959 --> 02:21.959
Yogi: There are one or two people coming.
Shri Mataji: They might come.

02:29.030 --> 02:36.030
Yogi: Only individuals. I invited a few people
at Ganapatipule and they said; ‘Oh, it’s

02:37.720 --> 02:44.720
such a long way.’ And I said: ‘But you
always expect us to come to yours.

02:47.670 --> 02:54.670
Shri Mataji: Yes. They have to move. Columbus
could go to America, why not you people go

03:14.980 --> 03:21.980
to Australia. Can’t understand.
Yogi: And a much more comfortable trip.

03:41.590 --> 03:48.590
Shri Mataji: Much more comfortable. They found
a much more comfortable place to live in.

04:21.090 --> 04:28.090
He was really lost. But in a way thank God,
you see. Otherwise there would have been no

05:25.729 --> 05:32.729
Indian left in India, if he had come here
by chance. So many flowers, beautiful. In

06:36.669 --> 06:43.669
Singapore I bought a book, very interesting,
called as: ‘Faces of Islam.’ And I was

06:47.139 --> 06:54.139
surprised that the whole concept of Islam
is Sahaja. Absolutely. And all the, authors

06:56.960 --> 07:03.960
and all the people, who have discussed there,
are saying that Muslims are not Islamic. They

07:06.479 --> 07:13.000
don’t follow Islam. That’s why their whole
thing has become so rigid. I mean so surprising

07:13.000 --> 07:17.940
that book has revealed to Me the confessions,
of these people.

07:17.940 --> 07:24.940
And the society that Mohammed Sahib has talked
about is ours. Muslims are nowhere. Absolutely

07:25.440 --> 07:32.050
the way He has described how the brotherhood
would be there, how righteousness would be

07:32.050 --> 07:38.259
there. But one thing is missing I feel, that
He said: ‘You must seek the knowledge. You

07:38.259 --> 07:44.180
must seek the Truth.’ Despite that, whatever
was Islam, they have failed to seek the knowledge,

07:44.180 --> 07:49.900
and to learn from others. Can you imagine?
And He has said how to deal with non-Muslims

07:49.900 --> 07:55.590
also. And they said that there are many who
are just minimal Muslims. Some of them are

07:55.590 --> 08:01.729
just for name’s sake, they are not Muslims.
I mean I was so amazed. We have such a misunderstanding,

08:01.729 --> 08:08.729
that I always said that all these Incarnations
and Prophets, came to establish a religion

08:08.919 --> 08:15.919
which was really Sahaja Yoga. All their expectations
were Sahaja Yoga. And they have deviated so

08:18.539 --> 08:23.860
much, that you start wondering what is this,
as in Christianity, you see. How much it has

08:23.860 --> 08:29.460
deviated, Christianity, to what level it has
gone, it is shocking, really shocking.

08:29.460 --> 08:36.460
I don’t know if you know of a book written
‘In God’s Name’. And in that book, it

08:38.599 --> 08:45.599
reads like a novel actually, I mean it’s
very interesting. In that book the writer

08:47.269 --> 08:53.449
has suggested that this present pope, is responsible
for the murder of the previous one. And there

08:53.449 --> 09:00.449
were thirteen or fourteen murders took place,
just to hide this. Can you believe it? And

09:01.629 --> 09:08.629
recently one of the persons was murdered was
Calvi. And they say, that this Calvi was murdered,

09:10.999 --> 09:17.110
I mean every week in Italy since I am there,
some new exposures are coming. But this Calvi

09:17.110 --> 09:24.110
was murdered in a way that he was hanged,
on one of the bridges of London. And if he

09:25.509 --> 09:32.509
was, he was the one, the one who murdered
him, he said that: ‘I am a member of mafia

09:36.790 --> 09:42.869
all right, but I was paid by this Vatican
by this pope, for murdering that man.’ Is

09:42.869 --> 09:49.869
a confession from him. And Mr Heard was, questioned:
‘Why didn’t you take action against this

09:51.410 --> 09:55.519
when these things happen in England?’ He
says: ‘What’s the use? Because they would

09:55.519 --> 10:02.519
kill all our lawyers, our judges everyone.
It’s all mafia.’ So the whole system of

10:02.679 --> 10:09.679
Catholic Church is nothing but mafia. Nine
million, dollars of counterfeit, were printed

10:12.679 --> 10:19.679
and were distributed through their bank, that
is Vatican Bank. Can you believe it? I mean

10:21.759 --> 10:28.759
this is Christianity. Is this what Christ
preached? Killing people, doing all kinds

10:29.019 --> 10:30.119
of things?

10:30.119 --> 10:36.199
I mean nowhere I find Mohammed decrying anyone.
He said: ‘You have to believe in everyone’.

10:36.199 --> 10:42.360
Only these people are saying, that He was
the last. He went to this limit to say that:

10:42.360 --> 10:49.360
‘I am not Divine. I follow the Divine laws
but I am not Divine.’ May be just He wanted

10:49.619 --> 10:56.619
people to follow. Surprising I was really
surprised that, if Koran is teaching such

10:59.220 --> 11:06.220
great things, the Muslims are just on the
other side of it and they admit, that Islam

11:07.269 --> 11:14.269
should not be confused with Muslims. In the
same way we can say that Christianity should

11:16.850 --> 11:23.850
not be confused with Christians. What about
Judaism? Same thing. I mean nowhere in that

11:25.559 --> 11:31.569
religion taught, to be like this the way they
are behaving. They are following Hitler, out

11:31.569 --> 11:38.569
and out. The one who killed them, tortured
them, they are becoming just like them.

11:38.699 --> 11:45.699
So what to say about these human beings as,
under the name of God, under the name of religion,

11:50.239 --> 11:55.119
behaving like this. The reason they have given
many: ‘Because of this and because of that.’

11:55.119 --> 12:02.119
So, this aspect, that they are saying that:
‘Because the people didn’t read Koran

12:10.970 --> 12:17.970
properly, they didn’t understand properly,
they should have been educated properly.’

12:19.519 --> 12:26.519
It will take thousand years to educate every
Muslim about it. And if they think that by

12:40.989 --> 12:47.670
teaching through their Book, it will be imbibed,
it’s not possible. Everybody reads Bible

12:47.670 --> 12:53.939
everybody reads Koran, but nothing goes inside
just reading reading reading. So their idea

12:53.939 --> 12:58.470
is that if they read and analyze, I mean you
have to have big universities for that, it

12:58.470 --> 13:05.470
could be taught to people and, still then
not necessary, that they would imbibe.

13:08.160 --> 13:14.649
I know of Mahatma Gandhi, see He was a Realized
soul was a, and He was of course, over-disciplined

13:14.649 --> 13:21.649
according to Me. And He put these ideas on
to His followers. As long as He lived they

13:23.709 --> 13:30.160
were all right. As soon as He died, they came
out in their true colors. Everything dropped

13:30.160 --> 13:36.689
off like some sort of a mud on their body,
and they became horrible people in India.

13:36.689 --> 13:43.689
So the thing missing is this, that, they are
not Realized souls. Because they are not Realized,

13:45.669 --> 13:50.619
all these things they cannot bear. They cannot
bear money, they cannot bear power. Now I

13:50.619 --> 13:57.619
think they cannot bear the religion. So you
have to have your Realization. Unless and

14:00.309 --> 14:03.829
until you have your Realization, you cannot
bear anything.

14:03.829 --> 14:10.829
Moreover in Sahaja Yoga I mean there are no
compulsions, no disciplines as such, I mean

14:11.029 --> 14:18.029
compared to what we see in all these religions.
Suddenly I find people coming up, to the expectations

14:21.209 --> 14:28.209
of righteousness, goodness, and they are also
very compassionate. So the change has come

14:31.959 --> 14:38.959
from inside, that means it’s the innate,
change. The innate religion has been awakened.

14:39.720 --> 14:45.259
It’s not just forced on you, that you should
be Vishwa Nirmala Dharmis but you become,

14:45.259 --> 14:51.410
you just become that. This is the point you
will see, these Prophets did not know, I think

14:51.410 --> 14:56.359
Christ did not know that these people will
never change unless and until they get their

14:56.359 --> 15:02.879
Realization. I think He knew also because
He always said that you have to be born again.

15:02.879 --> 15:09.689
So when He said: ‘You are to be born again,’
they have a, brand you see again, one are

15:09.689 --> 15:14.679
Christian, another Born Again, another are
Seventh Day, another, something. All just

15:14.679 --> 15:16.040
the same stupid people.

15:16.040 --> 15:23.040
But Sahaja Yoga is the only way. Where what
you, say that’s what you follow. Practice

15:25.829 --> 15:32.470
and precepts are just the same for Sahaja
Yogis. They just can’t do it something else.

15:32.470 --> 15:36.759
They are dreaming also that the occident had
a very bad influence on Islam and all that.

15:36.759 --> 15:42.470
I don’t think it’s that. You are coming
from the occident, still you have jumped into

15:42.470 --> 15:49.470
the right culture of religion, when you understand
what is righteousness what is good. You can

15:51.079 --> 15:58.069
bear it. You’re not to be told do this,
do that, but in the light of your Spirit you

